snippet.title: King Bullseye: The Chess Strike - Trailer
snippet.description:
The king is tired of being protected so now he is shooting the enemies down! King Bullseye is a shoot-the-target game in which the enemies are chess pieces on the board! Can you think quickly to predict who you need to destroy first? Headshots eliminate faster and earn more points!

Wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1600870/
